志偉賭馬賭位置<br />\n柒碌成龍成碌柒<br />\n成龍久別九龍城<br />\n靚女生日生女靚<br />\n我屌你呀你屌我<br />\n唐寧訓街訓靈堂<br />\n黑飽嬌個嬌飽黑<br />\n含撚怪搵怪撚含<br />\n高僧慾望慾增高<br />\n油麻地滿地麻油<br />\n溝女無錢無女溝<br />\n溝女冇樓冇女溝<br />\n腸粉食完食粉腸<br />\n大院高官睾丸大<br />\n成龍久别九龍城<br />\n大埔空姐胸部大<br />\n本日行程行日本<br />\n乳大淘尻淘大乳<br />\n老馬識桃色瑪瑙<br />\n愛港力無力講愛<br />\n靈芝送贈宋芝齢<br />\n行路草搵草路行<br />\n我愛你時你愛我<br />\n露體吳尊唔睇路<br />\n擦鞋飛哥飛鞋擦<br />\n送禮克勤乞禮送<br />\n夜出中環中出夜<br />\n星星頭成頭星星<br />\n冇腦貂貚雕老母<br />\n唐寅恨食杏仁糖<br />\n灣仔Jason J 仔彎<br />\n阿基諾用諾基亞<br />\n老夫子被子俘虜<br />\n法國有沒有國法</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f2699831c1b7be2ce3cf64f4114b6450c1720a3","tid":86163,"uid":36019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T06:39:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我屌你呀你屌我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我屌你時你屌我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78da9a2e0329087dfba27407a4b09d32b67c07e9","tid":86163,"uid":1049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T07:03:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">金毛西人西毛金</span></span>"},{"pid":"f16d72241ebdeb02af5312a32b4bdfbce12c29db","tid":86163,"uid":57979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T07:03:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>柒豬樓主豬咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed0aeea284875166635c3e62b0af86f379b8f56","tid":86163,"uid":22824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T07:18:02.000Z","msg":"伍伯賣唱賣百五"},{"pid":"24af049ec54cb35f8725907a7e68c939c8e2f9d7","tid":86163,"uid":5734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T07:22:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[隱藏]<br />\n食屎叮噹叮屎食<br />\n仆街大雄大街仆<br